40:18.947 --> 40:30.105
And I really believe that if you look at the conditions of our world today and everything that's going on and you look at the Bible and you read the word of God, Jesus is fixing to come back and get us.

40:30.125 --> 40:31.146
You know what he says to us?

40:31.187 --> 40:35.193
He says this, and so much the more is you see the day approaching.

40:35.213 --> 40:38.578
And so many times we use that as faithfulness to church.

40:38.850 --> 40:43.176
And we say, you know what, the Lord's coming, so we better be faithful to church.

40:43.557 --> 40:46.461
And I agree with that, but it's more in the verse.

40:46.922 --> 40:51.689
It's not just faithfulness to church, but it's this, exhorting one another.

40:53.711 --> 41:00.201
Exhort image either reason why, because the closer we get to the coming of God, the worse it's going to get.

41:00.221 --> 41:06.610
It's going to get worse and worse and worse and worse.

41:06.786 --> 41:08.588
the closer we get to the coming of the Lord.

41:08.849 --> 41:09.430
So you know what?

41:09.450 --> 41:11.973
We need to do more and more and more.

41:12.253 --> 41:15.137
We need to go to church more and more and more.

41:15.438 --> 41:19.403
And when we get to church, we need to exhort one another.

41:20.825 --> 41:22.848
We need to encourage one another.

41:23.709 --> 41:25.571
I try my best.

41:25.591 --> 41:33.162
I try my best every Sunday when the choir's coming down to find somebody and go, you knocked a home run this morning.

41:34.564 --> 41:36.306
Man, you sung good this morning.

41:36.802 --> 41:38.023
That was amazing.

41:38.424 --> 41:39.945
Thank you for being in your place.

41:40.526 --> 41:41.227
You know what that is?

41:41.687 --> 41:43.309
It's just encouraging.

41:43.329 --> 41:47.653
And he says, and so much the more as you see today approaching.

41:47.673 --> 41:50.717
So in closing, I think we could honestly say this.

41:51.557 --> 41:55.462
If we really look at the scripture, we're to be doing all of these things.

41:56.763 --> 41:59.486
God's given us the ability to do all of them.

41:59.506 --> 42:03.570
Some we may do better than others, but we should be doing all of them.

